headline: July Ignites at Jimmy's Jazz & Blues Club
summary: This July, the stage at Jimmy's Jazz & Blues Club lights up with the heat of summer and the soul of America's greatest music traditions. Whether you're kicking off the long weekend with live music, or looking to extend the fireworks past the Fourth of July, Jimmy's has your summer soundtrack covered. From blistering blues and funky throwdowns to modern jazz, our lineup this month is packed with unforgettable performances in the heart of downtown Portsmouth.
